<strong>PENALTY FOR VIOLATION:</strong>
<p>In the case of Vacation category students who do not vacate their rooms =
as per the above, the following actions will be taken<br>
a) A penalty charge of Rs. 300/- per day will be levied.<br>
b) The rooms occupied violating the instructions will be opened in the pres=
ence of Hostel Management authorities.&nbsp; All effects found in the rooms=
 will be removed and stored in cloak rooms without any responsibility on Ho=
stel Management.<br>
c) The Hostel Management Authority reserves the right to take further disci=
plinary action against the students who violate the rules.&nbsp; Such disci=
plinary actions will include:<br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (i) Denial of Rooms in the coming semesters<br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(ii) Denial of single occupancy privilege.<br>
d)&nbsp; Vacation Category students must handover the room compulsorily dur=
ing office working hours
</p>
